{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/705770/extras/Story.png?t=1701343057\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/705770/extras/SoloJohanna.png?t=1701343057\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/705770/extras/Monty2.png?t=1701343057\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">An endless nightmare awaits Johanna Prokuri!</h2>She was once a prodigy, capable of creating powerful automatons and other machines.<br>But three years ago, she lost her creativity during a nightmare.<br><br>One day a charming mole named Montgomery appears in her dreams. <br>He warns her that a Dream Demon &quot;cursed&quot; her with something known as the Mare Noctem. <br>The loss of her creativity is just one of the symptoms and she's about to turn into a monster soon.<br><br>Now the duo is hunting Dream Demons together and try to find a way to get rid of her curse before it's too late.<br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/705770/extras/Features.png?t=1701343057\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>An interactive combat system with action commands. Aim with your skills and evade enemy attacks.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/705770/extras/Combat.png?t=1701343057\" /><br></li><li>Build and personify your battle machine to fight off Dream Demons. Find a way for \u201cmore inspiration\u201d to unlock additional modules.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/705770/extras/ConstructMonty.png?t=1701343057\" /><br></li><li>Many characters, all with their own goals, fears and dreams. You can bond with them if you deem it necessary, maybe it pays off to be nice?</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/705770/extras/Quirky.png?t=1701343057\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A big plot tree which allows to see the whole story from different angles.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/705770/extras/Endings.png?t=1701343057\" /><br></li><li>Dogs which can be pet.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/705770/extras/WG_D_Minie_Bark02.png?t=1701343057\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Many special boss battles, all with their own high quality soundtrack.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/705770/extras/Nimarus.png?t=1701343057\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Wegi","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/705770/eb8b34338d108068149d401d52b74cc0403eb1bf.jpg"},{"name":"Just nineteen, a dream obscene","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/705770/d4d05eeb89bf2bee9d51564611cc84079d01c6f9.jpg"},{"name":"Kaleidoscopic Mind","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/705770/e9ff3e41f87090425096c5051ad808343ef62c6e.jpg"},{"name":"Lie Lie Lie","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/705770/b1951bccf4a663e3e01da25e5e157f72292eb9c1.jpg"},{"name":"FOXXIEEE!!!!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/705770/535e4cb85e25255e7e0ee45b40264422e2d005b2.jpg"},{"name":"Die Geister die ich rief","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/705770/19d25adb4963ec4edcca9433ef9802490a173d7a.jpg"},{"name":"Life is simply unfair, don't you think?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/705770/669d55c9287768110d17ffb67cc3b7586aac8159.jpg"},{"name":"Loud like Love","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcom